Place the credit card to the right of the set of keys on the edge of the table.
Turn around and move back to the nightstand to the right of the bed in the corner of the room.

Turn around and move to the foot of the bed then turn and face the table to the left of the door.
Place the credit card to the left of the yellow pencil on the edge of the table closest to you.
